  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q91",
  "body": "How do the sacraments become effectual means of salvation?\n\nThe sacraments become effectual means of salvation, not from any virtue in them, or in him that doth administer them; but only by the blessing of Christ, and the working of his Spirit in them that by faith receive them.",
